  "decision_conditions": [
    "REASON: The proposed mansard roof extension by reason of its design, siting, height and scale would be a prominent and visible roof development resulting in a discordant and unsightly feature in the streetscene, detrimental to the character and appearance of the host building and the terrace.  The development is contrary to policies 7.4 (Local character) and 7.6 (Architecture) of the London Plan 2011, policies CS8 (Enhancing Islington’s Character) and CS9 (Protecting and enhancing Islington’s built and historic environment) of the Core Strategy 2011, policies D4 (Designing in Context) and D11 (Alterations and Extensions) of the Islington Unitary Development Plan 2002 and section 2.4.3 (Rooflines with Existing Alterations/Extensions) of the Islington Urban Design Guide 2006."
